title: Miss Seventeen
overview: Miss Seventeen puts 17 accomplished and ambitious young women in a Manhattan loft to compete in weekly character-testing challenges, all under the watchful eye of "Seventeen" magazine editor-in-chief Atoosa Rubenstein. The winning girl will receive a prize package including a college scholarship and a paid internship at "Seventeen". None of the contestants are strangers to success, but will they be able to keep their cool when the stakes get high?
